# Image Prediction using a Standalone Wasm Binary on GCP

```elixir
Mix.install([
  {:nx, "~> 0.5.1"},
  {:nx_image, "~> 0.1.0"},
  {:kino, "~> 0.8.1"},
  {:req, "~> 0.3.5"},
  {:benchee, "~> 1.1.0"},
  {:wasmtube, github: "kentaro/wasmtube", branch: :main}
])
```

