## Prediction with Wasm binary

```elixir
resnet50_wasm = Wasmtube.from_file("/home/antipop/elixir-ml-wasm/wasm/resnet50.wasm")

result =
  resnet50_wasm
  |> Wasmtube.call_function("predict", image: kino_image.content, width: 224, height: 224)
```

